divs: Sighting DetailsI laid down to go to bed and i was laying there staring out the window when i saw a white, seemingly large object that flew straight very fast. Boomerang-shaped, all white. tips were thinner than the middle. no sound and nothing like i had ever seen. this was the same summer as my other report of a different object, though this was completely different. it left my sight very fast. i was scared, but it seemed to be flying towards the sky but not straight up, so i felt like if it was an alien, it was leaving.
